<div type="translation"><ab>
			<lb n="1"/>
		[In the n]ame of Go[d, the Compassionate, the Merciful].
			<lb n="4"/>
		There is no god but God [alone, He has no associate;]
			<lb n="5"/>
		He has not begotten, neither was He begot[ten and He has none that is like unto Him].
			<lb n="8"/>
		Muḥammad is the Messenger of Go[d, He has sent him with guidance and true religion].
			<lb n="9"/>
		The servant of God al-Walîd, [Commander of the faithful].
			<lb n="12"/>
		This belongs to that which was decreed by the Amîr [ʿAbdallâh son of ʿAbd al-Malik]
			<lb n="13"/>
		in the year [eighty nine.]
</ab></div>
